1. *Slučaj*no se sreo svoj stari prijatelj. (By chance, he met his old friend.)
2. Oni su se suočili sa *slučajem* koji je bio izuzetno složen. (They faced a case which was extremely complicated.)
3. On je imao običaj da se ponaša kao u *slučaju* da je gospodar. (He had a habit of behaving as if he were the master.)
4. Nisu u potpunosti razumeli *slučaj*. (They did not fully understand the case.)
5. Ovo je bio izuzetan *slučaj*. (This was an exceptional case.)